Organic Compounds (VOCs) that are detectable by smell. 
BGC‚Äôs precautions follow industry standards, to limit exposure and ensure care for people‚Äôs 
health. Projects are underway in BGC to further limit exposure potential where required. 
1.2 Hazards 
 The component of highest concern is benzene due to its carcinogenic health risk.   
‚Ä¢ Consequently, Workplace Exposure Limit (WEL) and ambient air quality standards are set 
at very stringent concentrations. 
