2.3  BGC waste disposal is controlled by the Waste Consignment Note (WCN) (Appendix 1). 
All requests for waste handling and transport shall have a WCN.   
2.4  Waste shall be properly segregated based on their disposal routes. 
2.5  No waste materials from BGC activities shall be accepted at the waste facility unless the 
