final disposal/treatment destination. 
2.6  HSE Environmental Team shall be consulted if there is any uncertainty with the details of 
this procedure and/or if additional waste management training is required for the 
activity/location. 
2.7  Waste management planning, including waste identification, storage, schedule and 
disposal is important to minimize the waste generation and optimize the reuse, reduce 
and recycling of waste. 
