This WMP is not for: 
‚Ä¢ Portable equipment with flexible wiring and a plug under complete control of one 
person; 
‚Ä¢ Testing of energized electrical equipment or other electrical work. 
 Examples of energy or hazardous substances are: 
‚Ä¢ Gas or liquids under pressure; 
‚Ä¢ Flammable or toxic substances; 
